{"tid":688890,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"除左任達華，原來仲有個演員叫簡達華 🙄","createTime":"2018-06-03T15:40:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-04T10:47:56.000Z","uid":44730,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ed52d1ef89884d1b1b5bacd5eae28d1485d7f5a3","tid":688890,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T15:40:31.000Z","msg":"【曾拍《至尊計狀元才》】「西洋仔」簡達華腦癌病逝 終年61歲<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://video.appledaily.com.hk/mcp/encode/2018/06/03/3624401/20180603_ent_04_w.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvideo.appledaily.com.hk%2Fmcp%2Fencode%2F2018%2F06%2F03%2F3624401%2F20180603_ent_04_w.mp4&d=hpq7ZA7EHjIIdPpRstEu%2FC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=ce515c3c\" target=\"_blank\">https://video.appledaily.com.hk/mcp/encode/2018/06/03/3624401/20180603_ent_04_w.mp4</a>"},{"pid":"fc617cc6cce59f2b5c88b3b3c13357747548abe2","tid":688890,"uid":46035,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T15:43:11.000Z","msg":"原來仲有個演員叫曹達華<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9deebfdb651f02d480e7759bb0e57c90182d2020","tid":688890,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T15:43:27.000Z","msg":"仲有冇邊個達華？<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/04/133211_19a6a9085bc66dde26a8720afef6f892.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F04%2F133211_19a6a9085bc66dde26a8720afef6f892.png&h=e2c59df6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8b744eb832606a9745cd93aef37c046e42600d8a","tid":688890,"uid":76488,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T15:43:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c27b3e54a3b6e9edadd12af7ad3fba5083be9745","tid":688890,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T15:44:36.000Z","msg":"曾經喺90年代，被稱「西洋仔」嘅演員簡達華，前日（6月1日）於東華醫院因腦癌病逝，終年61歲。當年佢經常同劉德華、譚詠麟等合作，專演奸角，演出過嘅電影有《至尊計狀元才》、《肝膽相照》、《江湖情》、《至尊無上》、《猛鬼學堂》等共十多部電影。"},{"pid":"b3d39fa5d43a32852dcca4c3c13c2c9a4ebfb8f0","tid":688890,"uid":555,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T15:45:17.000Z","msg":"仲有個艾簡達拿"},{"pid":"45c0ee2bebd8fa44feab04c31358cedbd0c7bc6f","tid":688890,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T15:45:24.000Z","msg":"本身係澳門居民嘅簡達華，年幼時係孤兒，由養父養大，並跟養父姓簡。佢同現任太太結婚超過三十年，兩人育有一子一女。簡達華只拍咗十多部戲，之後轉行做生意，早年已經喺丹麥買下物業，兩名子女都喺丹麥讀書，算係生活無優。近年簡達華已退休，經常丹麥、澳門兩邊走，閒時又會返香港。"},{"pid":"9860c0d6135dfacbc44e7fc736090d1cbef2b51d","tid":688890,"uid":14208,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T15:45:26.000Z","msg":"腳趾達華"},{"pid":"5e2806361f3d7a16412cfcc02fccd6043e13bcc8","tid":688890,"uid":34701,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T15:48:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images.cdn.fourfourtwo.com/sites/fourfourtwo.com/files/styles/image_landscape/public/antoniocandreva-cropped_x6rd0aomi35o1a9sz0yoyac8r.jpg?itok=qeCdhxym&amp;c=87b6d99828d88c1b8ffe17a08d24fc7d\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.cdn.fourfourtwo.com%2Fsites%2Ffourfourtwo.com%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Fimage_landscape%2Fpublic%2Fantoniocandreva-cropped_x6rd0aomi35o1a9sz0yoyac8r.jpg%3Fitok%3DqeCdhxym%26c%3D87b6d99828d88c1b8ffe17a08d24fc7d&h=d2d9ef68&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3ee3426a0e15dbc4baa6d70a1b17411c62483c52","tid":688890,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T15:52:31.000Z","msg":"上google打簡達華，點知搵到 安東尼奧&middot;<span style=\"color: red;\">簡達華</span> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">😂</span><br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;（Antonio Candreva，1987年2月28日－）是一位意大利足球運動員。出生在羅馬。目前效力於意甲球隊國際米蘭。"},{"pid":"b704404f9078fb9d7a0933952bd290457f7ce4e4","tid":688890,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T15:55:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">【演過黃秋生手下】常和劉德華合作 簡達華92年後再沒作品</span><br />\n<br />\n大家可能對他的印象不太深，但如果說是「西洋仔」，可能有點印象，他曾經拍過《肝膽相照》、《鬼新娘》、《江湖龍虎門》、《江湖情》、《猛鬼學堂》、《江角卡門》、《富貴開心鬼》、《至尊無上》、《第一繭》、《專釣大鱷》、《至尊計狀元才》、《絕橋智多星》、《無敵幸運星》、《賭城大亨之新哥傳奇》。<br />\n<br />\n在多套電影中專演奸角，演過黃秋生的手下，又經常和劉德華、譚詠麟等合作。在92年的《賭城大亨之新哥傳奇》之後，簡達華都沒有其他作品。"},{"pid":"26acb1f0e3f7eadda9df30bd4adf6d64137da171","tid":688890,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T15:58:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有個艾簡達拿</blockquote><br />\n又有幾多個達拿？<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/04/133211_19a6a9085bc66dde26a8720afef6f892.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F04%2F133211_19a6a9085bc66dde26a8720afef6f892.png&h=e2c59df6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8eb5f5dc41e8dee9131cf24e4daf21cb7efe9cdf","tid":688890,"uid":555,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"26acb1f0e3f7eadda9df30bd4adf6d64137da171","tid":688890,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T15:58:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有個艾簡達拿</blockquote><br />\n又有幾多個達拿？<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/04/133211_19a6a9085bc66dde26a8720afef6f892.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F04%2F133211_19a6a9085bc66dde26a8720afef6f892.png&h=e2c59df6&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T15:59:17.000Z","msg":"費達拿"},{"pid":"7c3c85b6c627cc8c3c3c2d0cdd3a1e9642c7ec7e","tid":688890,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T15:59:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>腳趾達華</blockquote><br />\n暗星？<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/04/133211_19a6a9085bc66dde26a8720afef6f892.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F04%2F133211_19a6a9085bc66dde26a8720afef6f892.png&h=e2c59df6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"594831b51d48d3453cb683a24eb3333cb2bef932","tid":688890,"uid":35313,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T16:00:37.000Z","msg":"仲有駱達華"},{"pid":"