門》、《富貴開心鬼》、《至尊無上》、《第一繭》、《專釣大鱷》、《至尊計狀元才》、《絕橋智多星》、《無敵幸運星》、《賭城大亨之新哥傳奇》。<br />\n<br />\n在多套電影中專演奸角，演過黃秋生的手下，又經常和劉德華、譚詠麟等合作。在92年的《賭城大亨之新哥傳奇》之後，簡達華都沒有其他作品。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n旺角卡門毒果寫錯江角卡門？<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/04/133211_19a6a9085bc66dde26a8720afef6f892.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F04%2F133211_19a6a9085bc66dde26a8720afef6f892.png&h=e2c59df6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"86174f689c4e33c989b5da1df94ec3dc99fca384","tid":688890,"uid":81569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T01:09:16.000Z","msg":"之前pcll跟個位師父叫何達華<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n份人又鳩屎又孤寒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a33355867c82069b1e05735b5185ba29a4ae2e71","tid":688890,"uid":66113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T10:38:59.000Z","msg":"至尊計狀元才找數飲尿<br />\n江湖情同萬梓去殺周潤發<br />\n咁岩2套都叫西洋仔個樣又真係鬼鬼地所以對佢有印象<br />\n但google只係得踢波果個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nRIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a2b4fd7694999771a0d35c1329e101215e0f7a5","tid":688890,"uid":49197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T10:47:56.000Z","msg":"有個醫生叫薛慕華添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}